
 torero
 ======

Is a simple python script to facilitate search & discovery of torrent files
based on certain filtering.

Requires installed lxml library. Try with
> easy_install lxml

Written and tested on python 2.7

Torrents discovery and downloader called episodes.py is an example application,
written using torero.py module. Please note that script only finds and loads
the *.torrents files. You will have to import them into a torrent client for
downloading the payload data.

